{"word":"Ataroth","slug":"ataroth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ataroth</b> <a href=\"#/H5852\">H5852</a> <br/> Called also Atroth.<br/> 1. A city east of Jordan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=3'>Num 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=34'>Num 32:34</a><br/> 2. A city, or possibly two different cities, of Ephraim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=16&verse=2'>Jos 16:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=16&verse=5'>Jos 16:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=16&verse=7'>Jos 16:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=13'>Jos 18:13</a><br/> 3. A city of Judah, called Atroth-beth-joab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=54'>1Ch 2:54</a><br/> 4. A city of Gad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=35'>Num 32:35</a>"}]}